high_descs: Walk straight until the end of the gray couch and face the books on the couch.
Pick up the remote control from the couch.
Turn around and face the table in front of the couch.
Put the remote control near the plant on top of the table
Walk slightly to the right, go straight and turn left to go to the TV.
Pick up another remote control from the TV cabinet.
Turn around, walk straight and turn right to go back to the table.
Put the remote control on top of the table
anns.task_desc: Put 2 remote controls on the table in front of the couch.

high_descs: Take a step right and walk to the right side of the couch you see on your left then turn to face it.
Pick up the remote you see in front of you.
Turn around to face the coffee table.
Put the remote on the coffee table to the left of the statue in the center of the table.
Walk to the tv you see in front of you and stand facing it.
Pick up the remote on the tv stand to the left of the laptop.
Walk back to where you put the first remote.
Put this remote to the right of the statue to the right of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two remotes on the coffee table.

high_descs: look down and go straight to the seat of the gray couch closest to the window
pick up the remote off of the couch
turn all the way around to face the coffee table
place the remote on the coffee table
turn right and then left to the television stand
pick up the remote that is on the television stand
turn right and then right again to be on the other side of the coffee table
place the remote down in the top right corner of the table
anns.task_desc: place two remote controls on to the coffee table

high_descs: Go to the right and slightly forward, then turn to the left and go to the right side of the blue couch.
Pick up the remote control that is on the couch.
Turn around to the coffee table.
Place the remote on the coffee table to the left of the two statues.
Go around the coffee table and forward to the table with the TV on it.
Pick up the remote control off of the table.
Turn around and go back around to the other side of the coffee table.
Put the remote on top of the blue credit card that is on the right side of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put two remote controls on a coffee table.
